      "text": "And this is all due to the tremendous Nazi propaganda machinery, what Goebbels started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think people have a bad side within themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They like to see other people suffer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this gives me great pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And basically what great pain is caused by me, because I feel the tremendous loss of the people, the six million Jews who among themselves had many talented, tremendously talented men, women, and children, who could have been the next Einsteins or the next Mozarts of our century and their life was snuffed out doing the Holocaust.",
